<bibRefCitation author="Monzen, K." box="[1069,1272,818,845]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="15 - 21" refId="ref48520" refString="Monzen, K. (1953) Revision of the Japanese gall wasps with the descriptions of new genus, subgenus, species and subspecies (I). Cynipidae (Cynipinae), Hymenoptera. Annual Reports of the Gakugei Faculty of the Iwate University, 5, 15 - 21." type="journal article" year="1953">Monzen 1953: 15</bibRefCitation>
