<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="26" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="25.[151,1437,818,1133]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,891,917]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Remarks.</emphasis>
The alternating lifecycle was closed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Yukawa, J. &amp; Masuda, H." box="[780,1083,891,917]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" refId="ref55993" refString="Yukawa, J. &amp; Masuda, H. (1996) Insect and mite galls of Japan in colors. Zenkoku-Nouson-Kyoukai, Tokyo, 826 pp. [in Japanese]" type="book" year="1996">Yukawa &amp; Masuda (1996)</bibRefCitation>
and the sexual generation was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y." box="[300,502,927,953]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="812 - 830" refId="ref44445" refString="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y. (2016) First description of asexual generation and taxonomic revision of the gall wasp genus Latuspina (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 109 (5), 812 - 830. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / saw 051" type="journal article" year="2016">Ide &amp; Abe (2016)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[151,1437,818,1133]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,308,962,989]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Remarks (2).</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Yukawa, J. &amp; Masuda, H." box="[316,617,963,989]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" refId="ref55993" refString="Yukawa, J. &amp; Masuda, H. (1996) Insect and mite galls of Japan in colors. Zenkoku-Nouson-Kyoukai, Tokyo, 826 pp. [in Japanese]" type="book" year="1996">Yukawa &amp; Masuda (1996)</bibRefCitation>
photographed the sexual gall and described it as ‘Kunugi-mi-ko-togaritama-fushi’ (C-104), and the asexual gall as ‘Kunugi-ha-guki-ko-tama-fushi’ (C-081). Later, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y." box="[1227,1436,999,1025]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="812 - 830" refId="ref44445" refString="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y. (2016) First description of asexual generation and taxonomic revision of the gall wasp genus Latuspina (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 109 (5), 812 - 830. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / saw 051" type="journal article" year="2016">Ide &amp; Abe (2016)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned that these galls correspond to the sexual and asexual generations of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ide &amp; Abe" authorityYear="2016" baseAuthorityName="Ashmead" baseAuthorityYear="1904" box="[1034,1184,1035,1060]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Latuspina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atamiensis">
<emphasis box="[1034,1184,1035,1060]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">L. atamiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="26" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="25.[151,1437,818,1133]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,295,1070,1096]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Biology.</emphasis>
The acorn galls of the sexual generation and the dehiscent petiole galls of the asexual generation both develop on 
<taxonomicName box="[282,436,1107,1133]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="acutissima">
<emphasis box="[282,436,1107,1133]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Q. acutissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[490,631,1107,1133]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="variabilis">
<emphasis box="[490,631,1107,1133]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Q. variabilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(sect. 
<taxonomicName box="[706,778,1107,1133]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Cerris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[706,778,1107,1133]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Cerris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) (Table 1; 
<bibRefCitation author="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y." box="[900,1085,1107,1133]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="812 - 830" refId="ref44445" refString="Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y. (2016) First description of asexual generation and taxonomic revision of the gall wasp genus Latuspina (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 109 (5), 812 - 830. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / saw 051" type="journal article" year="2016">Ide &amp; Abe 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
